{"tid":206913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府倡急症室收費加至180元　普通科門診加至50元","createTime":"2017-04-18T15:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T16:00:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1352ce967681899e3622096ae8132b549d8d858","tid":206913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"政府倡急症室收費加至180元　普通科門診加至50元<br />\n<br />\n2017-04-18 HKT 22:40<br />\n 分享工具\t facebook  twitter<br />\n 政府建議增加公立醫院收費，其中建議急症室收費增至180元。（港台圖片）<br />\n政府建議增加公立醫院收費，其中建議急症室收費增至180元。（港台圖片）<br />\n   00:31     <br />\n 01:58      <br />\n文采揚報道<br />\n政府建議增加多項公立醫院收費，急症室由100元加至180元，低於醫管局建議的220元。普通科門診由45元增至50元，計劃今年年中實施新收費。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長高永文表示，建議要待行政會議通過才可落實。<br />\n<br />\n有學者分析，加價後的收費仍與私家醫生收費有差距，無助減少急症室求診人次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1325849-20170418.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1325849-20170418.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7f27210a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1325849-20170418.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=65fdb4a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1325849-20170418.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b57d1924a8c1cda739ce0955ba39fb83423a3f2c","tid":206913,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"實發實發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9daeb3b063fbf4b2123eb67c3669da119477fa22","tid":206913,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"R痕"}]}